Exports logs to [Tinybird Events API](https://www.tinybird.co/docs/forward/get-data-in/events-api).
The exporter supports back pressure handling by honoring `Retry-After` and
`X-RateLimit-Reset` headers returned by Tinybird when the service is
overloaded.
